{
  "stem": "6719.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe it was just me, but I think it affected everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were thirsty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the first thing we heard, don't drink.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You want to die?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Drink.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What do you mean you want to die?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't drink.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So don't drink.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's a command.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Don't drink, so we don't drink.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So here, this guy puts the number on there, tattoos the number on there, and then we go to the shower.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was the first and last shower I had in, I think, about four months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Blistering hot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so we got out, and, uh, we were assigned to, uh, certain parts to where we marched.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I went into the barrack number one, which was the-- where the tailor department was.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What's the tailor department?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The tailor department was what when you arrived and you got that number, you got your tattoo, and you got your clothing, you went there with all these things to number one down there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was a little-- not a desk-- a-- a-- a little anteroom with a desk-like thing, a piece of board.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was a guy standing behind it, and you gave him your clothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You gave him your number, and he gave it to somebody behind him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were about 10 of 12 machine operators down there, and they sewed on-- sewed a number on there, then gave it back, and then you went to somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So I'm a tailor, but I don't know anything about a sewing machine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "What skills [? they're ?] going to show?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I-- the kapo was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I said to him, I said, it's OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You speak German?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Perfect.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He said, OK, we need a guy like you around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "OK, I'm going ahead.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
